cast.overview: When Juli meets Bryce in the second grade, she knows it's true love. After spending six years trying to convince Bryce the same, she's ready to give up - until he starts to reconsider.
cast.title: Flipped

cast.overview: An adaptation of F. Scott Fitzgerald's Long Island-set novel, where Midwesterner Nick Carraway is lured into the lavish world of his neighbor, Jay Gatsby. Soon enough, however, Carraway will see through the cracks of Gatsby's nouveau riche existence, where obsession, madness, and tragedy await.
cast.title: The Great Gatsby

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia. Callan McAuliffe (born Callan Ryan Claude McAuliffe, on 24 January 1995) is an Australian actor. He starred in the American feature films Flipped and I Am Number Four.
